item.title: github
item.description: Error handling / エラー処理 git pull error: Your local changes to the following files would be overwritten by merge: Please commit your changes or stash them before you merge. Aborting git pullでマージエラーが発生した場合の対処です error: Your local changes to the following files would be overwritten by merge: test.py Please commit your changes or stash them before you merge. Aborting Solve it by overwriting 上書きして解決する場合 ullの元が正しい前提で上書きを行います。 git fetch origin master git reset --hard origin/master git pull origin/master
